Key Match Events: Devon Conway batted through the entire 20 overs to make 92 off 58
Glenn Phillips made a catch that will become the image of this very one-sided match
Glenn Maxwell hit a 95m six wrong-handed over cover (midwicket)
Tim Southee took the wicket of David Warner
Pre-Game Insights: This was the 13th match of Group 1
The match was played in Sydney on October 22, 2022, for the ICC Men's T20 World Cup
Post-Match Reflections: New Zealand last beat Australia in Australia in December 2011, they've finally followed it up with a performance that maybe makes it all worth it
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Kiwis were doing things that shouldn't be possible. Like flying.
Others: The match was played at the Sydney Cricket Ground
